PLAYER HELP
FOLLOW
Type ~CCOMfollow bob~CHLP to follow the person named 'bob'. Swap in the player name of someone whom you actually want to follow. This will allow you to chase a person around, although if they can run faster than you they will lose you pretty quickly.

You can see who is following you by typing ~CCOMfollowers~CHLP; similarly, you can see who you are following by typing ~CCOMleaders~CHLP.

See also: ~CREFunfollow~CHLP, ~CREFlose~CHLP
